Bespoke binding designed by Hugnet and fabricated by Christy: covers with goat leather, blind tooling, and foil blocking, front and back each holding liquid mercury and hand-cut glass shapes between two panes of glass (back cover accidentally cracked in 1940 causing mercury to be lost); decalcomania in gouache on paper endleaves; silk-ribbon bookmark.
CreditLine: Gift of Helen and Sam Zell
